om\": 673, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My daughter, Dana, had to carry his birth certificate with her a lot of times, just to prove that he was the same age as the kids that were wrestling.\\\"\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dana_Incorporated\", \"score\": 0.9340984049754103, \"rank\": 0.0677343856298813, \"text\": \"Dana\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dana_Incorporated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dana_Incorporated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Precords have seen him wrestle at the University of Michigan and in his hometown of Folwerville, Michigan.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"score\": 0.9927956682306625, \"rank\": 0.007255414290557328, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were in Folwerville this month as he rode in the Fourth of July parade.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is plenty to brag about: the Precords said Adam is a married man and has a master's degree in aerospace engineering.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really proud of him because he has been such a good kid growing up.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He worked hard with his dad and he's been so good with kids.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very proud of that young man,\\\" said Wayne Precord.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Wayne and Cherie will not be joining the family in Paris, due in part to health issues.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": 